Package de.oth.blocklib.ai.python.statemachine

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPythonAIState
    Represents a machine state
    The state contains one script path that is executed when this State is chosen as the current state of a state machine
    After the script finished the returned value can be used to determine the next state for the state machine
    AbstractPythonAIStateMachine
    A simple state machine that switches between python machine learning scripts
    The scripts used should return an int via sys.exit(number_here)
    ExamplePythonAIState
    An example implementation of a state
    ExamplePythonAIStateMachine
    An example implementation of the Script state machine
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    PythonScriptReturnState
    Possible states that a python ai script may end in
